{
  "name": "新進同仁電腦設備申請單",
  "path": [
    "IT01_資訊需求單",
    "資訊基礎服務處需求",
    "Helpdesk"
  ],
  "inputs": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "label": "報到月",
      "key": "onboard_month"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "label": "報到日",
      "key": "onboard_day"
    },
    {
      "$enum": "Text.STAFF_ID"
    },
    {
      "$enum": "Text.ENG_NAME"
    },
    {
      "$enum": "Text.CHI_NAME"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "label": "申請項目",
      "key": "device_for_freshman_item",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "筆記型電腦 (新機需於ISE設定mac address)"
        },
        {
          "text": "桌上型電腦"
        },
        {
          "text": "桌上型外接螢幕"
        },
        {
          "text": "TOKEN"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "label": "需求說明",
      "key": "device_for_freshman_description",
      "template": "[需求說明]\n本單位新進同仁，預計於${onboard_month}月${onboard_day}日報到，人員資訊如下\n新進同仁員編: ${staffId}\n新進同仁中英文姓名: ${engName}/${chiName}\n\n申請以下設備，以符合作業需求\n\n${device_for_freshman_item}\n( V )配合新進同仁電腦設備配發，HelpDesk 將依此需求更新ISE mac address 資訊\n\n[執行單位]\n問管暨IDC作業管理部"
    }
  ]
}